class Test:

    @staticmethod
    def text():
        return 'test'
with mock.patch.object(app.ui.nameList, 'currentItem', return_value=Test):
    with mock.patch.object(PyQt5.QtWidgets.QMessageBox, 'question',
        return_value=PyQt5.QtWidgets.QMessageBox.Yes):
        with mock.patch.object(app.app.mount.model, 'deleteName',
            return_value=True):
            with qtbot.waitSignal(app.app.message) as blocker:
                suc = app.deleteName()
                assert suc
                assert ['Model [test] deleted', 0] == blocker.args
